></table></figure><p>最后发现了uploads文件夹中存在我们上传的文件，这里我上传的是kali自带的webshells -&gt; php shell</p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610015215297.png" alt="image-20240610015215297"></p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610015226580.png" alt="image-20240610015226580"></p><p>获得shell之后发现当前用户的家目录存在一个备份文件的目录，备份用户是root，备份的文件是刚刚上传的文件</p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610015420778.png" alt="image-20240610015420778"></p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610015456626.png" alt="image-20240610015456626"></p><p>上传<a href="https://github.com/DominicBreuker/pspy">pspy64</a>监听一下本地运行的程序，这期间可以再次上传文件以快速触发备份脚本</p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610015815107.png" alt="image-20240610015815107"></p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610015840007.png" alt="image-20240610015840007"></p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610015919950.png" alt="image-20240610015919950"></p><p>发现root用户一直在执行我们当前用户的备份脚本，查看这个文件发现我们可以编辑</p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610020009008.png" alt="image-20240610020009008"></p><p>修改脚本内容为 chmod +s &#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash</p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610020049370.png" alt="image-20240610020049370"></p><p>等待一段时间查看&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash已经拥有SUID权限了，直接运行&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash -p获得root权限</p><p><img src="/./vulnyx-diff3r3nts3c/image-20240610020229005.png" alt="image-20240610020229005"></p>]]></content>
    
    
